  "texts": [
    "The space of Stokes representations and the wild character varieties with irregular class Θ have a similar form as those with irregular class Θ.",
    "Let us first describe the new formal data.",
    "Each of the active circles of Θ is again subdivided into four distinguished intervals.",
    "Via the Legendre transform, these intervals are",
    "The Stokes local system before Fourier transform."
